The test matrix "tols4000" is described in [1], and can be obtained from
Matrix Market [2] and from the University of Florida Sparse Matrix
Collection [3].

[1] Z. Bai, D. Day, J. Demmel, and J. Dongarra. A test matrix collection
    for non-Hermitian eigenvalue problems.  Tech. rep. 1996.
[2] http://math.nist.gov/MatrixMarket/data/NEP/mvmtls/tols4000.html
[3] http://www.cise.ufl.edu/research/sparse/matrices/Bai/tols4000.html
